{"profile":{"awsPrograms":[{"category":"AI Hero","joinedAt":2020.0,"memberStatus":"ACTIVE","programName":"HERO"}],"basicInfo":{"alias":"rustemfeyzkhanov","avatar":"https://avatars.builderprofile.aws.dev/2xojZbp9Nrxis0psq3fGtVNR0X8.webp","bio":"Rustem Feyzkhanov is the Engineering Manager for the Snorkel AI Platform team, building data-centric AI solutions. His background includes roles as ML Engineering Manager at Instrumental (manufacturing AI) and an engineer at Astro Digital (satellite imagery AI).\n\nA prominent voice on leveraging cloud infrastructure for AI, Rustem is the author of the book “Serverless Deep Learning with TensorFlow and AWS Lambda.” He is a seasoned speaker who has shared his expertise at numerous prestigious conferences, including O'Reilly Strata, O'Reilly Software Architecture, and AI DevWorld. His presentations focus on the practical application of cloud-native AWS services for building efficient and scalable deep learning training and inference pipelines.\n\nIn addition to his professional and speaking engagements, Rustem is the creator of several popular open-source repositories on GitHub that provide valuable resources for the community. His current interests lie in pushing the boundaries of serverless for AI/ML, tackling the unique challenges of hosting large language models (LLMs), and engineering robust, production-grade ML workflows using AWS infrastructure.","builderProfileId":"b11e4e7d-801c-4843-8f99-e7aae49dd18a","createdOn":1.713331503104E12,"headline":"","isStaff":false,"name":"Rustem Feyzkhanov"},"location":{"displayLocation":{"countryRegion":"US"}},"profileStatus":"ACTIVE","socials":{"blog":"https://ryfeus.medium.com/","devto":"https://dev.to/ryfeus","github":"https://github.com/ryfeus","linkedIn":"https://www.linkedin.com/in/ryfeus","twitter":"https://www.twitter.com/ryfeus","youtube":"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC3aX3qJTV7JXdOgNPv7x3WQ"}}}